Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "pošten" in different forms and positions:

1. *Pošten* čovek uvek govori istinu. (An honest person always tells the truth.)
2. On je veoma *pošten* prema svojim prijateljima. (He is very honest with his friends.)
3. Njegova *poštena* narav ga je učinila omiljenim među kolegama. (His honest nature has made him popular among his colleagues.)
4. Ova kompanija je poznata po svojoj *poštenoj* poslovnoj praksi. (This company is known for its fair business practices.)
5. *Pošteno* je priznati svoju grešku. (It's honest to admit your mistake.)
6. Ne možemo očekivati da će svi ljudi uvek postupati *pošteno*. (We can't expect everyone to always act fairly.)

I hope these examples help!